  <a class="thesis-row clickable" href="./fashion-decision-layer/index.html">
    <div class="t-num">01</div>
    <div class="t-inner">
      <div class="t-tag">
        <span class="t-category">Fashion &amp; Commerce</span>
        <span class="t-badge live">Live</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="t-title">The Fashion <i>Decision Layer</i></h3>
      <p class="t-desc">Value in fashion is shifting from selling products to owning the system that determines what consumers wear, access, and buy. The commerce stack is being rebuilt around decision infrastructure, not inventory.</p>
      <div class="t-cos">
        <span class="t-co">Pickle</span>
