        <span class="t-badge live">Live</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="t-title">The <i>Personal Health OS</i></h3>
      <p class="t-desc">Consumer healthcare is shifting from episodic to continuous. The constraint was never technology, it was trust. Physician-supervised AI creates the only durable moat at the clinical threshold.</p>
